Name: Club Life
About the game: Sean is in his final year of school, close to the time for him to head off to college, his plans to keep his head down this year and avoid complications are ruined when his teacher demands he join two clubs if he wants her to write him a recommendation for college. With his hands tied there are only a few choices for him to start his Club Life.
